snippet.title: Paw Paw Paw Trailer 1
snippet.description:
Paw Paw Paw is a 2D side scroller beat 'em up game under development by Simpleton.

It took place in a fantasy world inhabited by walking, talking, and sentient animals, where the king has gone mad with power. You play as the resistance in their attempt to slay the king of Paw Paw Paw.

For more information please visit http://simpleton.rocks/pawpawpaw
